er had a place.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aEnlightenmentzGreat Britain. 0aFaith and reasonxHistory. 0aInternet of things. 0aOccultismzGreat BritainxHistoryy17th century. 0aOccultismzGreat BritainxHistoryy18th century. 0aScience and magicxHistory. 0aSkepticismzGreat BritainxHistoryy17th century. 0aSkepticismzGreat BritainxHistoryy18th century. 0aSpiritualismzGreat BritainxHistoryy17th century. 0aSpiritualismzGreat BritainxHistoryy18th century. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Great Britain / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishz978311070473008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020z9783110704525oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311069231040uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300249460?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300249460423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300249460/original  a978-3-11-069231-0  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-070471-6  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070473-0  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishb2020  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020